AI Website Builder FAQ

What is an AI website builder?

An AI website builder is a tool that uses artificial intelligence to help you create a website in just a few minutes. Wix’s AI website builder helps you quickly create best-in-class sites through a conversational interface. Once your site has been generated by our AI, you have the flexibility to easily adjust the theme, layout, images, and text until you are satisfied with the result.


Read more: How does AI work?

How do I choose the best AI website builder?

As you consider which AI website builder is best for you, keep the following key factors in mind:


  • Design quality: Your AI website design should be unique, customizable and complete with the pages, content, features and tools essential for your industry. Choose a builder that has done market research and understands what businesses like yours require.


  • Ease of use:  An ideal builder balances AI assistance with user-friendly controls, so you can achieve your desired outcome quickly and intuitively.


  • Scalability: Ensure that the site you build can grow alongside your business and handle increased traffic, complex features and additional page creation. Your builder should provide the tools you need  to support every step of your creation journey.


  • Added value features: Some AI website builders, like Wix, stand out by offering enterprise level infrastructure with benefits like reliable security, free hosting, industry leading performance and 24/7 support. Plus, Wix offers business and website solutions in one place complete with domains and   built-in marketing, SEO and business management tools.

Why should I build my website with AI?

Building a website with AI offers several key advantages. These benefits include:


  • Quick creation: AI-powered tools can generate complete websites in minutes, saving you significant time and effort.


  • User-friendly: AI website builders are designed for non-technical users, which makes creating professional-looking sites accessible to everyone regardless of skill level.


  • Cost-effective: Many AI-powered site creators offer free plans. Some platforms also include built-in tools that offer the functionality you need without having to pay for third party apps.

How do I create a website with AI?

You can create a website using AI by simply following these four steps:


1. Sign up for our free AI website builder: Answer a few setup questions about the type of website you're creating to get started.


2. Review your site’s brief: Based on your answers, the AI site builder will create a detailed description of what your website is all about, what it will include, and how it will look and feel.


3. Refine your site: You can interact with the AI and refine the brief until you are happy with the results. Once your site has been generated, you can continue to prompt the AI to change the site theme, layout, text, images, and more.


4. Continue working on your site in the editor: Once your site has been generated with AI, you can further customize each of your site elements directly from the editor.

Can I use the Wix AI website builder for free?

You can start building your site with AI for free. If you wish to connect custom domains, collect payments online, or access additional features, you'll need to choose a Premium Plan.

Can I customize the design of my AI-generated website?

Personalization is at the heart of our AI website builder. Your website is crafted according to your preferences, guided by the information you provide. After you have reviewed your site and made sure that it meets your requirements, you can continue to fine-tune the layouts, themes, and more until it's perfect.


Even after your site is generated, you retain full control. You can always further customize each element of your website design directly from the Wix Editor.

How long does it take to create my site with AI?

Our AI website design generator significantly speeds up the site creation process. In just moments, it crafts a fully functional website customized to your specific needs. You can seamlessly collaborate with the site builder, experimenting with various themes, layouts, and more, until your site is an exact reflection of your vision.


Read more: How long does it take to build a website

Is a site created with AI mobile-friendly?

Yes, websites generated using the Wix AI site generator are designed to be mobile-friendly. This means your site will automatically adapt to different screen sizes and devices, providing an optimal user experience on desktop and mobile devices.

Will my AI built website be optimized for SEO?

All Wix sites have SEO friendly infrastructure and a variety of built-in SEO tools that can help you follow Google’s SEO best practices, and increase your chances of better ranking on search results pages. These tools include:


  • AI Meta Tag Creator: Use AI to create search-optimized title tag and meta description suggestions in seconds based on your site content. Choose from three primary suggestions, or refine suggestions to better match your brand and audience.


  • SEO Assistant: Get a tailored checklist of recommendations on how to optimize your site's pages for search engines, as well as recommendations on how to improve your page's content, structure, and SEO attributes. The SEO Assistant also identifies potential issues with your page and creates tasks to help you to resolve them.


  • Sitemap Submission & Site Inspection: With Google Search Console integration, you can streamline site indexing and troubleshoot SEO issues directly from your site dashboard. According to a recent Google study, these built-in features increased traffic by 15% for Wix users.


  • Structured data markup: Add structured data to your site's pages to help enhance your website's visibility on Google search results. Create and add your own structured data, or, save time and effort by using pre-created structured data to your site pages.


  • Flexible 301 redirect options: Avoid 404s and potential lost traffic with auto redirects on static pages—and more—or set individual, group and bulk 301 redirects.

Are hosting and domain included when creating my site with AI?

When you create a website using the Wix AI site builder, it automatically comes with multi-cloud, reliable hosting. When you upgrade your site to any Wix Premium Plan, you’ll receive a voucher for a free domain of your choosing for one year.

What other AI tools are available on Wix?

Once you create your site with the AI website builder, Wix has a variety of built-in AI tools available to you in the editor that can help you further customize and improve many elements of your site.


Wix’s AI tools include:

What is Wix ADI?

Wix ADI (Artificial Design Intelligence) is the first generation AI-powered website design tool that Wix released. Since 2016, ADI has offered a quick, intuitive way to build websites. Building a website with ADI begins by making a series of selections about your website’s requirements and design preferences. ADI then presents design options based on these inputs, allowing for some level of customization, while significantly simplifying the design process for users who prefer an easier, more guided approach.
